<br>
Then I got my epic.<br>
<br>
I changed my mind, the effect wasn't good, it was excellent.  <br>
<br>
I've had druids, necros, shaman, even enchanters tell me they wish their epic had Barrier of Force.<br>
<br>
I would rank the Wiz epic probably third or fourth in overall rankings.   Cleric and Enchanter could be called the second or third best epics, since they definately enhance the class, but they really aren't too much 'fun' for the cleric/enchanter.  It just makes you a better buffwhore. =)   But the wizzy one is fun, it's nice to be able to soak up damage.<br>
<br>
Number one epic?  Oh, that's easy.  The Magician epic.  It's a bitch to complete, but man, it's worth it.  Mage with epic is MILES above a mage without.  It fits the class perfectly.<br>
